{"type": "article", "id": 28524, "title": "多功能灯具", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-22T06:53:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153300gBfYlKHutRSMvPIz.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>来自伊斯坦布尔的建筑师和灯光艺术家 <a href=\"http://busratunc.com/\">Buşra Tunç</a> 和创意互动平台 <a href=\"http://atolyeistanbul.co/#atlye\">Atölye</a> 联手打造了一款可以适应各种室内设计的灯具 Lamalight。设计师的创作灵感来源于单条横线，弯管之间则采用了定制设计的 270 度可旋转不锈钢接头，可以展开成各种造型，在台灯、壁灯或者吊灯间转换，满足不同场合的需要。折叠型的设计使得它更便于包装和运输，看上去简约又紧凑。Lamalight 此前在米兰设计周上首次亮相，未来会在 Kickstarter 上展开众筹。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153257yBW5oVXg14khHEAx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153257h0seBvCznkp3RH51.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153258DgLBFHk1CyEpTrSw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153259bCf49cljk51XwJ7Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}